ZXASCII
AUTO -1
PROG turtle shapes
10 REM Turtle shapes
20 LET sx=SCRw/2,sy=SCRh/2: RADIANS: PAPER 0: INK 3
30 FOR k=1 TO 180 STEP 15: FOR j=0 TO 36000 STEP 1440/k: CLS: MOVE sx,sy: FOR n=1 TO 200: INK n: DRAW 5+n: ROTATE 15+j/1000: DRAW 10+n: ROTATE j: WAIT SCREEN: PALETTE SHR 1,1 TO 255: NEXT n: WAIT SCREEN: NEXT j: NEXT k
